{"tid":1603912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【要贏只有呢個終極方法】","createTime":"2019-09-29T20:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T16:58:21.000Z","uid":228437,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"094441cdea326edecd45385736e4d64108fee870","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:35:21.000Z","msg":"手足們，想贏嗎？<br />\n<br />\n721果日係我感覺最多勇武既一日<br />\n721果日終於有一個大家都認同既口號好振奮到人心<br />\n721果日好多前線一個手術口罩，硬食tg都無走<br />\n721果日我地仲未受到大搜捕所以真係好好好齊人<br />\n<br />\n一切都返唔到轉頭喇各位手足<br />\n依家我地食少左好多TG，因為班狗次次都開槍<br />\n依家我地少左轉場 因為已經再無一個交通工具可以載我地<br />\n依家我地少左好多真勇武，因為佢地好多已經被捕，被關押，受傷，流亡，被性侵，失蹤，什至死亡<br />\n<br />\n手足們；<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地已經輸左好多好多野，香港已經返唔到轉頭架喇，再驚，我地只會萬劫不復。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地無退路架啦，只有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">進攻</span></span></strong>才先係我地唯一出路，手足們，為我地被捕，被虐，被性侵，受傷，被流亡，被自殺同逝去既所有義士同烈士，我地一齊1212，唔係後退，而係1212<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">進攻</span></span></strong>，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n和理非朋友們，我地願意做<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">矛</span></strong>，你地願認為我地做<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盾</span></strong>嗎？唔駛捱打，係我地撤退既位置，幫我地指罵黑警，幫我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拖延時間</span></strong>，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">請大家睇下以下既相，唔好忘記我地既所有手足既付出。<br />\n勇武進攻，和理非防守，我地一齊贏，一齊走，好嗎？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ce1q0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ce1q0v.jpg&h=7a98616d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LL3p8dR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLL3p8dR.jpg&h=e9f8aa8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XG6nUTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXG6nUTR.jpg&h=1f247197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeyhJNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeyhJNc.jpg&h=74edca75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZxnasd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZxnasd.jpg&h=a7e3f0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDd1yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouDd1yT.jpg&h=f1194811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjK1q0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjK1q0z.jpg&h=f80ad3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g98ajkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg98ajkA.jpg&h=42f93647&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4n41q0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4n41q0B.jpg&h=b118dbda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXi2ash.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXi2ash.jpg&h=394e13cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac9016fe90fd43de9a38ea974713afdf241bd267","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa73590d9c452074c17c64faea65d1088c841d27","tid":1603912,"uid":45979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:37:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d1225e37eece1a6285c5cf33e7c78054458279b","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:37:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ddda6206db0787219d49d9040aaf2f730383244","tid":1603912,"uid":214113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:37:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"272ac0d0a7064dd245839b98a1ce006d30f192c9","tid":1603912,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:37:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">點都要打落去<br />\n因為</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-siz