":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8f35e1acbd7d18c2d24a0277a41fea7965873f9","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"027ec9172ce55e07a5e19af2199dce84fec3b603","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:48:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7a8e9f3823893f632087ef27d862ceb723dd4a4","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef837621dbdc2c526b929da2270b2ef5db05441d","tid":1603912,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"10月1號 賀佢老母！"},{"pid":"c8bbce72f612ba1d98fcece04705a1599fdfaae2","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"338754004de85494e37abcc42a77ea7beb124401","tid":1603912,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:41:46.000Z","msg":"我會試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:50:03.000Z","msg":"試下啦，求下你啦，我地係最後一代香港人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地死曬，無曬香港人架喇"},{"pid":"add5adc4df5612e518590ceedb313e883168d7bc","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:50:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f53f94cf489162cf4e495a9a3b1349219e4ecb3a","tid":1603912,"uid":220627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd5e7211ddb3835b50e54ba9481a7e3ddd344b24","tid":1603912,"uid":309757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:51:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83464ee7d33766eaa85754522d91760bf3d07109","tid":1603912,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfd38e2d5e7b6c9f0305e2c341da626b35b5541","tid":1603912,"uid":288812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:51:56.000Z","msg":"💥💥💥大大力Share💥💥💥<br />\n<br />\n轉自tg <br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<br />\n1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..<br />\n<br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<br />\n6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..<br />\n<br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n大家share比手足同連登"},{"pid":"1686568b40ad792a8069e2859d4ab73a6f3c3ba9","tid":1603912,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bbce72f612ba1d98fcece04705a1599fdfaae2","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"338754004de85494e37abcc42a77ea7beb124401","tid":1603912,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T20:41:46.000Z","msg":"我會試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" 