，幫我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拖延時間</span></strong>，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">請大家睇下以下既相，唔好忘記我地既所有手足既付出。<br />\n勇武進攻，和理非防守，我地一齊贏，一齊走，好嗎？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ce1q0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ce1q0v.jpg&h=7a98616d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LL3p8dR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLL3p8dR.jpg&h=e9f8aa8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XG6nUTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXG6nUTR.jpg&h=1f247197&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeyhJNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeyhJNc.jpg&h=74edca75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZxnasd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZxnasd.jpg&h=a7e3f0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDd1yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouDd1yT.jpg&h=f1194811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjK1q0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjK1q0z.jpg&h=f80ad3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g98ajkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg98ajkA.jpg&h=42f93647&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4n41q0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4n41q0B.jpg&h=b118dbda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXi2ash.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXi2ash.jpg&h=394e13cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5edf206d50966f934cb6be11ceea5b8a2017a8a9","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00: