時收集完再傳俾前線<br />\n其他物資照舊<br />\n可以分散風險<br />\n不過唔知係咪大部分前線都會玩火魔法<br />\n前線可唔可以話俾大家聽可以點幫 帶啲咩 做咩好<br />\n<br />\n或者一人一樽漂白水/其他腐蝕性水<br />\n拿撚死垃圾防暴popo"},{"pid":"46a819014f7994e161367769796ffd4e0f48c4ca","tid":1603912,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2029f08638c4d928a161042622201dfa949fac6c","tid":1603912,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"當警察set 好防線就要退，轉陣<br />\n<br />\n千其唔級正面攻除非對家少人"},{"pid":"eed5a39b7230796a09a61e659b32d2b7b51683ce","tid":1603912,"uid":14916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dcac4870d629d0d65429129e97bf5075bd701f6","tid":1603912,"uid":321626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"1d4a748f738b1226c72965d945c526eeaec24f64","tid":1603912,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"762f6a2109f004aa51b346216ca45dd243597501","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f12fb687906caf4ab00f2aea2c850287edff1d0","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"131335a73e12732e7d7285401d3dd9ed9bcdb244","tid":1603912,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24ba630afd63174c080cd27648b395290c4be9c2","tid":1603912,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"不嬲示威就代表係進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察係保護市民同財產<br />\n警察一向係防守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e509a6a72c148b4904a0a6412ec09b634d291c0